      "title": "Come January 2021 our students and educators need to have a safe...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-1/cp0/c20.0.50.50a/p50x50/118284446_1181187205597451_4408149288731870177_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=m3IJEaWfp1AAX8owTVw\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ae50f33dffe903ce6d274a6e2f76ccea\u0026oe=5FD0DA1E\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003eDenver School Board Director - Tay Anderson\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/posts/1245018222547682\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eCome January 2021 our students and educators need to have a safe plan to return to school. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e It’s time for us to acknowledge that COVID will be around for the foreseeable future, but it’s also time for us to begin a plan that follows the science AND welcomes our students back to schools. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e I will be working with my colleagues on a plan that we can get in the hands of \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/teamdps\"\u003e#TeamDPS\u003c/a\u003e on what our future looks like moving forward in the coming weeks.\u003c/p\u003e",
      "date_published": "2020-11-10T15:18:26-07:00",
      "date_modified": "2020-11-10T15:18:26-07:00",
      "author": {
        "name": "Tay Anderson"
      }
    },
    {
