      "title": "Regardless of politics, I hope that we can be able to model for...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-1/cp0/c20.0.50.50a/p50x50/118284446_1181187205597451_4408149288731870177_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=m3IJEaWfp1AAX8owTVw\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ae50f33dffe903ce6d274a6e2f76ccea\u0026oe=5FD0DA1E\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003eDenver School Board Director - Tay Anderson\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/photos/a.257357004647147/1244875412561963/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eRegardless of politics, I hope that we can be able to model for our future generations that bullying and threats are not who we are as a society. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e As someone who has struggled with mental health issues and battled suicidal thoughts as a teenager, I am yet again reminded that we have a lot of work to do to support our communities. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e Hate has no place in our communities, I not only will pray for this individual I will begin to look at ways to improve mental health supports for students and staff in Denver Public Schools.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/photos/a.257357004647147/1244875412561963/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p280x280/124837219_1244875415895296_3916132855970235551_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=110474\u0026_nc_ohc=PwV16eLeMMEAX-r6BMB\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026tp=6\u0026oh=2b7fae7c5e346196d2a0fe18b40f7321\u0026oe=5FD0BFC3\" alt=\"Image may contain: text that says 'Cody Bentley 10:13 AM Hey dumbass Trump is still your president and will remain in office. Do us all a favor and swallow a barrel of a gun.'\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" caption=\"Image may contain: text that says 'Cody Bentley 10:13 AM Hey dumbass Trump is still your president and will remain in office. Do us all a favor and swallow a barrel of a gun.'\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/votinginformationcenter/\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003eSee the results and other info about the 2020 US Election. See Election Results\u003c/a\u003e",
      "date_published": "2020-11-10T11:08:23-07:00",
      "date_modified": "2020-11-10T11:08:23-07:00",
