      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-1/cp0/c20.0.50.50a/p50x50/118284446_1181187205597451_4408149288731870177_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=m3IJEaWfp1AAX8owTVw\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ae50f33dffe903ce6d274a6e2f76ccea\u0026oe=5FD0DA1E\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003eDenver School Board Director - Tay Anderson\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/photos/a.257357004647147/1240508026332035/\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eOne year ago Denver voters elected me to serve on the Denver School Board. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e We won with one of the largest margins in Denver history with 67,213 votes and I’ve been hard at work for the people of Denver. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e Thank you, Denver!\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/photos/a.257357004647147/1240508026332035/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/123946645_1240508029665368_200849000703586211_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=110474\u0026_nc_ohc=2cW_l04hds8AX-03Dl5\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-1.fna\u0026tp=6\u0026oh=4efc70b937828da95b52a7369f11335b\u0026oe=5FD2B1B9\" alt=\"Image may contain: 1 person, text that says 'ONE YEAR SINCE BEING ELECTED TO THE DENVER SCHOOL BOARD! 67,213 VOTES THREE MORE YEARS JUSTICE PEACE, .OVERTURNING CURRICULUM REQUIRE COURSES INFUSED WITHETHNIC STUDIES DENVER SCHOOL LEADERS ASSOCIATI RECOGNIZED ASA UNON PUBLIC SCHOOLS. INCLUSION RESOLUTION, REQUIRING DENVER PUBLIC SCHOOLS TO DENVER VOTE, ALLOWING VOTE SCHOOL BOARD ELECTIONS. DEFUNDED DENVER POLICE FROM DENVER SCHOOLS, INCREASING FUNDING FOR MENTAL HEALTH, NURSES, AND RESTORATIVE PRACTICES UPDATEDST USING HANDBOOK RESPONSIBLE OWNERSHIP PROGRAM FROM MOMS DEMANDA ACTION. AFFIRMED OUR COMMITMENT REOPENING REBEL FROM TAY ANDERSON DENVER SCHOOL BOARD AT-LARGE RETIRED DENVER SOUTH HIGH ONE YEAR SINCE BEING ELECTED TO THE DENVER SCHOOL BOARD!'\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" caption=\"Image may contain: 1 person, text that says 'ONE YEAR SINCE BEING ELECTED TO THE DENVER SCHOOL BOARD! 67,213 VOTES THREE MORE YEARS JUSTICE PEACE, .OVERTURNING CURRICULUM REQUIRE COURSES INFUSED WITHETHNIC STUDIES DENVER SCHOOL LEADERS ASSOCIATI RECOGNIZED ASA UNON PUBLIC SCHOOLS. INCLUSION RESOLUTION, REQUIRING DENVER PUBLIC SCHOOLS TO DENVER VOTE, ALLOWING VOTE SCHOOL BOARD ELECTIONS. DEFUNDED DENVER POLICE FROM DENVER SCHOOLS, INCREASING FUNDING FOR MENTAL HEALTH, NURSES, AND RESTORATIVE PRACTICES UPDATEDST USING HANDBOOK RESPONSIBLE OWNERSHIP PROGRAM FROM MOMS DEMANDA ACTION. AFFIRMED OUR COMMITMENT REOPENING REBEL FROM TAY ANDERSON DENVER SCHOOL BOARD AT-LARGE RETIRED DENVER SOUTH HIGH ONE YEAR SINCE BEING ELECTED TO THE DENVER SCHOOL BOARD!'\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e",
