      "title": "Appreciate folks for joining us again for a town hall. I...",
      "content_html": "\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://scontent.fapa1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-1/cp0/c20.0.50.50a/p50x50/118284446_1181187205597451_4408149288731870177_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102\u0026ccb=2\u0026_nc_sid=dbb9e7\u0026_nc_ohc=m3IJEaWfp1AAX8owTVw\u0026_nc_ht=scontent.fapa1-2.fna\u0026tp=27\u0026oh=ae50f33dffe903ce6d274a6e2f76ccea\u0026oe=5FD0DA1E\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/\"\u003eDenver School Board Director - Tay Anderson\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Tay2019/posts/1235668980149273\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com\"\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003eAppreciate folks for joining us again for a town hall. I understand not all questions may have been answered and I am always open to talk to folks regardless if we agree or not. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e I want to thank the parents, educators, and community for their words. We hard from folks from Lowry, Central Park, Montbello, and Green Valley Ranch. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e Your voices tonight helped guide me and others on how we can do better.\u003c/p\u003e",
